
1) Build an ATM abstraction:
Abstract class ATM with method process()
Withdraw and Deposit must override process()
Call using parent reference.
-->abstract class ATM {

    abstract void process();
}

class Withdraw extends ATM {

    void process() {
        System.out.println("Processing Withdraw");
    }
}

class Deposit extends ATM {

    void process() {
        System.out.println("Processing Deposit");
    }
}

public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        ATM a;

        a = new Withdraw();
        a.process();

        a = new Deposit();
        a.process();
    }
}


